 neutral composition in the cometary coma only when the ion\ndensities are significantly controlled by photon and photoelectron impact\nionization of neutrals rather than by the ion-neutral chemistry.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Dec 2020 18:28:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-06"}
