 on the host galaxy.\nThere is a substantial difference in the length of the misalignment lifetime\ndepending on the origin, and it can be explained by the magnitude of the\ninitial position angle offset and the physical properties of the galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Dec 2020 19:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-02"}
