tained are averaged over $E_{\\rm in}$. The averaged value is $r_{m}({\\rm\nEXP})=3.697$fm. Eventually, we obtain $r_{\\rm skin}({\\rm EXP})=0.023$fm from\n$r_{\\rm m}=3.697$fm and $r_p({\\rm EXP})=3.685$fm of electron scattering.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Dec 2020 21:02:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-17"}
